{
  "stem": "15991.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was delighted to leave finally and, and start, start my life in a way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, you're just reminding me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There had been talk of sending me to a residential school to be trained, and with children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very much looking forward to this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents had written away for brochures.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the day before I was supposed to leave, my parents decided that they couldn't afford it and that I had to stay at Corringway after all, and was not, could not do this, to me, wonderful seeming opportunity of getting on with my life.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was hard because my cousin, my brother, and my other cousin all went to school regularly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My cousins were evacuated, one cousin was evacuated, because of the bombing, with his school, and my older cousin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was always wonderful to have her come home from-- from school and-- and bring along tales of what she had learned in school and the books they had read and for me to get a little glimpse of education, which I really craved very much.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was quite a disappointment, not being able to go to this residential school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I continued.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in touch with my friends, but I had friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was not very much socialization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course there was a great deal of-- of bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And life just wasn't natural, wasn't the same because you had the bombs flying during the day and at night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, in order for us to be-- feel safer, we almost, all of us, except my grandfather, gathered in the living room downstairs and slept on mattresses there.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
